column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/f05fa03e8bfe806eae60c1de4a7780efa5aa8e04 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
Why are you naming the spacers specifically? We never refer to them. This is really over-doing things. If you keep them at the default spacer1 2 3 names you never have to rename them.\n
You are right (and I won't name them again), but as they now have the wrong name ;)...\n

So if you rename them anyway, please just name them verticalLayout / verticalLayout2 / etc and remove the _Wallet _Network part. Naming them specifically just gives extra maintenance (and review) effort without a good reason. Same for the label change below.\n
